Examples


Shows how to improve the quality of a rendered document with SaveOptions. autodoc=MakeObject<Document>(MyDir+u"Rendering.docx");
autobuilder=MakeObject<DocumentBuilder>(doc);

builder->get_Font()->set_Size(60);
